txt.en: 'I want out of this prison, [placeholder]. I do not belong here, locked up. I will help you drive out the nasty Orcs if you help me.\n\n'I need the key to this cell. Look for the jailors, kill them, and take their keys. If you free me, I will help you.'
'No keys to my cell? Curse the name of Kaushar! Curse him by the darkest things in the earth! Curse him!\n\n'I must think. I will gnaw the rat's guts out!'
'One of these jailors must have the keys to my cell!'
The goblin Oghûk wants you to help him escape from his cell.
Deliver the keys to Oghûk in his cell within the Goblin-town prison

Goblin-jailors can be found in the dungeons of Goblin-town.\n\nOghûk believes that the jailors in the Goblin-town prison have the keys to his cell. He wants you to kill the jailors and find the keys. Only after you free him will he help you.
